    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "DEPARTURE\nThe times shown on the Flight Coupons are the\nFlight Departure Times. You are requested to\narrive at the Airport or Town Terminal not later\nthan the time stated hereon. Upon arrival at\nAirport, please report at the counter as soon as\npossible in order to permit the completion of\nGovernment formalities.\nFLT.\nCOUPON\n1\nCHECK IN TIME\nAIRPORT\nTOWN\nADDRESS OF AIRPORT/DOWN TOWN\n3\n4\nARRIVAL\nUpon arrival, please reconfirm your reservations in\nperson, by telephone or by other means to the\noffice of carrier on which you have connecting\nreservations. At the same time, please advise\nthe office concerned of your local address to\nenable easy contact with you.\nENDORSEMENTS\n2015,1687770",
      "PASSENGER TICKET\nAND\nBAGGAGE CHECK.\nISSUED BY\n1313-00328\nJAPAN AIR LINES\nMEMBER OF INTERNATIONAL AIR TRANSPORT ASSOCIATION\nNEW MARUNOUCHI BLDG., NO. 4, 1-CHOME, MARUNOUCHI, CHIYODA-KU, TOKYO, JAPAN\nEach passenger should carefully examine this ticket, particularly the Conditions on the next page."
